Name: blepharocheilodontic syndrome 1
Definition: A blepharocheilodontic syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the CDH1 gene on chromosome 16q22.

Name: blepharocheilodontic syndrome 2
Definition: A blepharocheilodontic syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the CTNND1 gene on chromosome 11q12.
